title: A Daughter's Legacy - Virginia Smith.epub
description: To receive her inheritance and make peace with her late mother, Kelli Jackson must abide by the woman's will. Even though it means working as a zookeeper for six months--with animals that terrify her. How can she possibly explain her fears--and her past--to her handsome boss, Jason Andover? The glimpses of kindness-- and painful secrets--she sees in his eyes slowly have her sharing "everything." But then she makes a startling discovery--one that may tear them apart forever. Unless she can return the gift of love he's given her.
